# Walkthrough - GTM Migration and Event Tracking Integration

The application has been successfully migrated to Google Tag Manager (GTM). All global custom event tracking requirements, including route context mapping (`journey_string`) and first-party user data telemetry, have been fully implemented and verified.

## Changes Made

### 1. Global GTM Setup
- **[layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/app/layout.tsx)**: Removed `<GoogleAnalytics>` components and replaced them with `<GoogleTagManager gtmId="GTM-KZVN2H5N" />`.

### 2. Form Telemetry & Enhanced Conversions
- **[HeroQuoteForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/forms/HeroQuoteForm.tsx)**: Added tracking for successful short form submissions. Fires a `submit_partial_lead` event including the requested services, routing telemetry, and first-party user data (`user_email` and `user_phone`). It also accepts an optional `placement` prop to override placement categorization.
- **[DynamicQuoteForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/forms/quote/DynamicQuoteForm.tsx)**: Configured successful checkout form submission tracking. Fires a `submit_final_booking` event containing the minimum price range array value (`value`), routing context, currency (`'AUD'`), and user identifiers (`user_email`, `user_phone`, and `user_name`).
- **Form Placement Propagation**:
  - Updated **[Header.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/layout/Header.tsx)** to pass `placement="header_modal"` to the popup quote form.
  - Updated **[HeroSection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/home/HeroSection.tsx)** to pass dynamic `placement` (`hero_form` or `lp_hero_form` based on pathname).
  - Updated **[CtaStrip.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/home/CtaStrip.tsx)** and **[QuoteDialog.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/QuoteDialog.tsx)** to pass `placement="cta_strip_modal"`.
  - Updated **[contact/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/app/contact/page.tsx)** to pass `placement="contact_form"`.

