- **[FloatingCallButton.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/layout/FloatingCallButton.tsx)**: Tracks WhatsApp clicks (`whatsapp_click`) and floating button call clicks (`phone_call`).
- **[Header.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/layout/Header.tsx)**: Tracks phone number link clicks in both the header and the mobile menu drawer (`phone_call` event with `placement: "header"`).
- **[Footer.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/layout/Footer.tsx)**: Converted to a Client Component to enable path context tracking, and added `phone_call` tracking on the main footer telephone link (`placement: "footer"`).
- **[PromoPopup.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/home/PromoPopup.tsx)**: Added call link click tracking (`phone_call` event with `placement: "promo_popup"`).
- **[HeroSection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/home/HeroSection.tsx)**: Converted to a Client Component, added call CTA tracking (`phone_call` event).
- **[CtaStrip.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/home/CtaStrip.tsx)**: Added Call CTA link click tracking (`phone_call` event with `placement: "cta_strip"`).
- **[DynamicQuoteForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/forms/quote/DynamicQuoteForm.tsx)**: Tracks the phone link click at the bottom of the checkout page (`phone_call` event with `placement: "booking_form"`).

### 4. Promotion Popup Triggers
- **[PromoPopup.tsx](file:///c:/Users/alexr/Desktop/kinstel%20work/gold-coast-cleaners/src/components/home/PromoPopup.tsx)**:
